    "system": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<p><em>A small ball of bat guano floats into your hands and catches fire, then shoots forward. When it reaches its destination, it explodes.</em></p><p><strong>Dexterity</strong> <strong>Save</strong> </p><p>The fire spreads around corners, igniting flammable objects in the area that aren't being worn or carried, which take [[/damage 1d10 fire]] damage every round until extinguished as an action.</p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> Target takes [[/damage 8d6 fire]] damage*.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> Half damage.</p></li></ul><p></p><p><strong>*Upcasting:</strong> Increase damage by [[/damage 1d6 fire]]{1d6} for each spell level above 3rd.</p><p><em>Some objects may be too large or flammable to be simply extinguished as an action, and will require creative solutions.</em></p>",
            "chat": "<strong>Dexterity</strong> <strong>Save</strong> </p><p>The fire spreads around corners, igniting flammable objects in the area that aren't being worn or carried, which take [[/damage 1d10 fire]] damage every round until extinguished as an action.</p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> Target takes [[/damage 8d6 fire]] damage*.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> Half damage.</p></li></ul><p></p><p><strong>*Upcasting:</strong> Increase damage by [[/damage 1d6 fire]]{1d6} for each spell level above 3rd.</p>"
